Package com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport

Contains classes and interfaces for commands that make changes to data in the Analysis Repository.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ICommand A command that can be issued to the command service to perform a specific operation.
IItemChangeSetCommand A command that makes changes to the Cards of an Item.
 

Class Summary
AddCardToItem The IItemChangeSetCommand for adding a Card (as defined by a CardChangeSet) to an Item.
AddLatestItemsToSet The ICommand for putting the latest versions of multiple Items into a set.
AddSpecificItemsToSet The ICommand for putting specific versions of multiple Items into a set.
AmendCardOnItem The IItemChangeSetCommand for amending a Card (as defined by a CardChangeSet) on an Item.
AmendLink The ICommand for amending a Link, rather than the Cards it contains.
CardChangeInfo Contains information about values on a Card that the server has created or modified during execution of a CommandList.
Command An abstract implementation of ICommand that other ICommand implementations should extend.
CommandList A sequence of ICommands from a particular client session that should be executed in order, according to the CommandListOptions in force.
CommandListOptions Indicates the options that apply to the Commands in a CommandList at execution time.
CreateEntity The ICommand for creating an Entity with an active lease.
CreateLink The ICommand for creating a Link between two Entitys.
DeleteCardFromItem The ICommand for deleting a Card from an Item.
DeleteItem The ICommand for deleting an Item.
ExecuteCommandsResult Contains information about the changes that have taken place as a result of executing a CommandList.
ItemChangeInfo Contains information about an Item that has been changed by a command.
MergedCardInfo Contains information about the identifier, property groups, and properties of a Card that was added to the target in a merge operation.
MergedPropertyGroupInfo Contains information about the identifier and properties of a PropertyGroup that was added to the target in a merge operation.
MergedPropertyInfo Contains information about the identifier of a Property on a Card that was added to the target in a merge operation.
MergeEntities The ICommand for merging one or more source Entitys into a target Entity.
MergeInfo Contains information about the Entitys and Cards that were affected by a MergeEntities command.
ModifiedProperty Details of a Property whose client-supplied value was modified by the server during execution of a CommandList.
ModifiedPropertyGroup Details of a PropertyGroup containing Propertys whose client-supplied values were modified by the server during execution of a CommandList.
ReleaseLease The ICommand for releasing a lease on an Item.
RemoveItemsFromSet The ICommand for removing multiple Items from a set.
SetItemPrimaryProperties The ICommand for changing the primary Propertys on an Item.
SetItemSecurityPermissions The ICommand for changing the security permissions on an Item.
TakeLeaseOnLatestItem The ICommand for taking a lease on the latest version of an Item.
TakeLeaseOnSpecificItem The ICommand for taking a lease on a specific version of an Item.
 

Enum Summary
CommandType Indicates the type of an ICommand, and provides a type-safe way to cast it.
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport Description

Contains classes and interfaces for commands that make changes to data in the Analysis Repository.
